    <string name="first_run_msg">
        <![CDATA[
        <H3>Welcome</H3>
        Please read the following important message from the app’s developer before you continue to use MedsStockTracker:
        <p> <big><b>MedsStockTracker is just a convenience tool. It should never be used as a primary tool to manage critical medicine supply.
            Never rely on it to remind you to restock critical medicines.</b></big></p>
        <p> MedsStockTracker is developed and maintained by just one person in my free time.
            This app is open source and free. It does not contain ads or any other monetization mechanism.
            As a result, it does not go through typical software quality assurance procedures and might crash,
            suffer data loss, miss alerts, or malfunction in other ways.</p>
        <p> By clicking the “I accept” button you assert that you understand this,
            and that you are going to use the app only as a convenience tool.
            If you do not accept, please click the "Decline" button, and simply uninstall the app.</p>
        ]]>
    </string>

